<!--l. 1869--><p class="noindent">Many commands allow you to specify a linetype with an explicit color. Terminal-independent color choice is only
possible for terminals that support RGB color or pm3d palettes.
<!--l. 1873--></p><p class="noindent">Syntax:
<!--l. 1876--></p><p class="noindent"></p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">...</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;{</span><span class="p">linecolor</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">lc</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;{&lt;</span><span class="p">colorspec</span><span class="o">&gt;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;&lt;</span><span class="p">n</span><span class="o">&gt;}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">...</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;{</span><span class="p">textcolor</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">tc</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;{&lt;</span><span class="p">colorspec</span><span class="o">&gt;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;{</span><span class="p">linetype</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">lt</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;&lt;</span><span class="p">n</span><span class="o">&gt;}</span></span>
<!--l. 1879--></pre>
<!--l. 1882--><p class="noindent">where <span class="cmmi-10">&lt;</span>colorspec<span class="cmmi-10">&gt; </span>has one of the following forms:
