</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;cntrparam</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;order</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="n">10</span></span>
<!--l. 8552--></pre>
<!--l. 8555--><p class="noindent">To select levels automatically, 5 if the level increment criteria are met: </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;cntrparam</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;levels</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;auto</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="n">5</span></span>
<!--l. 8559--></pre>
<!--l. 8562--><p class="noindent">To specify discrete levels at .1, .37, and .9: </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;cntrparam</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;levels</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;discrete</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">1</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="n">1</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="p">exp</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="n">1</span><span class="o">),.</span><span class="n">9</span></span>
<!--l. 8566--></pre>
<!--l. 8569--><p class="noindent">To specify levels from 0 to 4 with increment 1: </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;cntrparam</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;levels</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;incremental</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="n">0</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="n">1</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="n">4</span></span>
<!--l. 8573--></pre>
<!--l. 8576--><p class="noindent">To set the number of levels to 10 (changing an incremental end or possibly the number of auto levels):
</p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;cntrparam</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;levels</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="n">10</span></span>
<!--l. 8581--></pre>
<!--l. 8584--><p class="noindent">To set the start and increment while retaining the number of levels: </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;cntrparam</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;levels</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;incremental</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="n">100</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="n">50</span></span>
<!--l. 8588--></pre>
<!--l. 8591--><p class="noindent">See also <span class="cmbx-10">set contour (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-206000III"><span class="cmbx-10">141</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set contour --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-203002"></a> for control of where the contours are drawn, and <span class="cmbx-10">set clabel (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-201000III"><span class="cmbx-10">137</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set clabel --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-203003"></a> for control of
the format of the contour labels and linetypes.
<!--l. 8594--></p><p class="noindent">See also
<a href="http://www.gnuplot.info/demo/contours.html"><span class="cmtt-10">contours demo (contours.dem) </span></a>
and
<a href="http://www.gnuplot.info/demo/discrete.html"><span class="cmtt-10">contours with user defined levels demo (discrete.dem). </span></a>
<!--l. 8602--></p><p class="noindent">
</p><h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a id="x1-204000III"></a>Color box</h4>
<a id="Q1-1-404"></a>
<a id="dx1-204001"></a>
<!--l. 8613--><p class="noindent">The color scheme, i.e. the gradient of the smooth color with min_z and max_z values of <span class="cmbx-10">pm3d</span>'s <span class="cmbx-10">palette</span>, is drawn
in a color box unless <span class="cmbx-10">unset colorbox</span>.
<!--l. 8618--></p><p class="noindent"></p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;colorbox</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;colorbox</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">{</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">{</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">vertical</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">horizontal</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">{</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">default</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">user</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">{</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">origin</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;x</span><span class="o">,</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">y</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">{</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">size</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;x</span><span class="o">,</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">y</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">{</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">front</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">back</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">{</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">noborder</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">bdefault</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">border</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="p">line</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;style</span><span class="o">]</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">show</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;colorbox</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">unset</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;colorbox</span></span>
<!--l. 8630--></pre>
<!--l. 8633--><p class="noindent">Color box position can be <span class="cmbx-10">default </span>or <span class="cmbx-10">user</span>. If the latter is specified the values as given with the <span class="cmbx-10">origin </span>and
<span class="cmbx-10">size </span>subcommands are used. The box can be drawn after (<span class="cmbx-10">front</span>) or before (<span class="cmbx-10">back</span>) the graph or the
surface.
                                                                                         
                                                                                         
<!--l. 8637--></p><p class="noindent">The orientation of the color gradient can be switched by options <span class="cmbx-10">vertical </span>and <span class="cmbx-10">horizontal</span>.
<!--l. 8640--></p><p class="noindent"><span class="cmbx-10">origin x, y </span>and <span class="cmbx-10">size x, y </span>are used only in combination with the <span class="cmbx-10">user </span>option. The x and y values are
interpreted as screen coordinates by default, and this is the only legal option for 3D plots. 2D plots,
including splot with <span class="cmbx-10">set view map</span>, allow any coordinate system to be specified. Try for example:
</p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;colorbox</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;horiz</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;user</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;origin</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">1</span><span class="o">,.</span><span class="n">02</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;size</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">8</span><span class="o">,.</span><span class="n">04</span></span>
<!--l. 8647--></pre> which will draw a horizontal gradient somewhere at the bottom of the graph.
<!--l. 8651--><p class="noindent"><span class="cmbx-10">border </span>turns the border on (this is the default). <span class="cmbx-10">noborder </span>turns the border off. If an positive integer
argument is given after <span class="cmbx-10">border</span>, it is used as a line style tag which is used for drawing the border, e.g.:
</p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;style</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;line</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="n">2604</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;linetype</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">1</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;linewidth</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">4</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;colorbox</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;border</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="n">2604</span></span>
<!--l. 8658--></pre> will use line style <span class="cmbx-10">2604</span>, a thin line with the default border color (-1) for drawing the border. <span class="cmbx-10">bdefault </span>(which is
the default) will use the default border line style for drawing the border of the color box.
<!--l. 8664--><p class="noindent">The axis of the color box is called <span class="cmbx-10">cb </span>and it is controlled by means of the usual axes commands, i.e.
<span class="cmbx-10">set/unset/show </span>with <span class="cmbx-10">cbrange</span>, <span class="cmbx-10">[m]cbtics</span>, <span class="cmbx-10">format cb</span>, <span class="cmbx-10">grid [m]cb</span>, <span class="cmbx-10">cblabel</span>, and perhaps even <span class="cmbx-10">cbdata</span>,
<span class="cmbx-10">[no]cbdtics</span>, <span class="cmbx-10">[no]cbmtics</span>.
<!--l. 8669--></p><p class="noindent"><span class="cmbx-10">set colorbox </span>without any parameter switches the position to default. <span class="cmbx-10">unset colorbox </span>resets the default
parameters for the colorbox and switches the colorbox off.
<!--l. 8673--></p><p class="noindent">See also help for <span class="cmbx-10">set pm3d (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-265000III"><span class="cmbx-10">182</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set pm3d --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-204002"></a>, <span class="cmbx-10">set palette (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-274000III"><span class="cmbx-10">187</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set palette --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-204003"></a>, <span class="cmbx-10">x11 pm3d (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-492000IV"><span class="cmbx-10">316</span><!--tex4ht:ref: x11 pm3d --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-204004"></a>, and <span class="cmbx-10">set style line</span>
<span class="cmbx-10">(p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-301000III"><span class="cmbx-10">204</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set style line --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-204005"></a>.
</p><h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a id="x1-205000III"></a>Colornames</h4>
<a id="Q1-1-406"></a>
<a id="dx1-205001"></a>
<!--l. 8681--><p class="noindent">Gnuplot knows a limited number of color names. You can use these to define the color range spanned by a pm3d
palette, or to assign a terminal-independent color to a particular linetype or linestyle. To see the list of known color
names, use the command <span class="cmbx-10">show colornames (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-205000III"><span class="cmbx-10">141</span><!--tex4ht:ref: show colornames --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-205002"></a>. Example:
<!--l. 8687--></p><p class="noindent"></p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;style</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;line</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="n">1</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;linecolor</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;rgb</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="s">"sea-green"</span></span>
<!--l. 8689--></pre>
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a id="x1-206000III"></a>Contour</h4>
<a id="Q1-1-408"></a>
<a id="dx1-206001"></a>
<a id="dx1-206002"></a>
<!--l. 8703--><p class="noindent"><span class="cmbx-10">set contour </span>enables contour drawing for surfaces. This option is available for <span class="cmbx-10">splot </span>only. It requires grid data, see
<span class="cmbx-10">grid</span><span class="cmbx-10">_data (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-374000III"><span class="cmbx-10">235</span><!--tex4ht:ref: grid_data --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-206003"></a> for more details. If contours are desired from non-grid data, <span class="cmbx-10">set dgrid3d </span>can be used to
create an appropriate grid.
<!--l. 8708--></p><p class="noindent">Syntax: </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;contour</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">{</span><span class="p">base</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">surface</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">|</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="o">&nbsp;</span><span class="p">both</span><span class="o">}</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">unset</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;contour</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">show</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;contour</span></span>
<!--l. 8714--></pre>
<!--l. 8717--><p class="noindent">The three options specify where to draw the contours: <span class="cmbx-10">base </span>draws the contours on the grid base where the x/ytics
are placed, <span class="cmbx-10">surface </span>draws the contours on the surfaces themselves, and <span class="cmbx-10">both </span>draws the contours on both the base
and the surface. If no option is provided, the default is <span class="cmbx-10">base</span>.
<!--l. 8722--></p><p class="noindent">See also <span class="cmbx-10">set cntrparam (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-203000III"><span class="cmbx-10">138</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set cntrparam --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-206004"></a> for the parameters that affect the drawing of contours, and <span class="cmbx-10">set clabel (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-201000III"><span class="cmbx-10">137</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set clabel --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-206005"></a>
for control of labelling of the contours.
<!--l. 8725--></p><p class="noindent">The surface can be switched off (see <span class="cmbx-10">set surface (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-305000III"><span class="cmbx-10">207</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set surface --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-206006"></a>), giving a contour-only graph. Though it is possible to
use <span class="cmbx-10">set size </span>to enlarge the plot to fill the screen, more control over the output format can be obtained by writing
the contour information to a file, and rereading it as a 2D datafile plot:
<!--l. 8731--></p><p class="noindent"></p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">unset</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;surface</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;contour</span></span><span class="p">
