<!--l. 9581--><p class="noindent">Except for the non-numerical formats, these may be preceded by a <span class="cmtt-10">"</span>0<span class="cmtt-10">" </span>(<span class="cmtt-10">"</span>zero<span class="cmtt-10">"</span>, not <span class="cmtt-10">"</span>oh<span class="cmtt-10">"</span>) to pad the field length
with leading zeroes, and a positive digit, to define the minimum field width (which will be overridden if the specified
width is not large enough to contain the number). The %S format also accepts a precision specifier so that fractional
seconds can be written. There is a 24-character limit to the length of the printed text; longer strings will be
truncated.
<!--l. 9589--></p><p class="noindent">Examples:
<!--l. 9591--></p><p class="noindent">Suppose the text is <span class="cmtt-10">"</span>76/12/25 23:11:11<span class="cmtt-10">"</span>. Then </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;format</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;x</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="C">#</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;defaults</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;to</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;"12/25/76"</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;\n</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;"23:11"</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;format</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;x</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="s">"%A,</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="s">&nbsp;%d</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="s">&nbsp;%b</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="s">&nbsp;%Y"</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="C">#</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;"Saturday,</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;25</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;Dec</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;1976"</span></span><span class="p">
</span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;format</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;x</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="s">"%r</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="s">&nbsp;%D"</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="C">#</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;"11:11:11</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;pm</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;12/25/76"</span></span>
<!--l. 9597--></pre>
<!--l. 9600--><p class="noindent">Suppose the text is <span class="cmtt-10">"</span>98/07/06 05:04:03.123456<span class="cmtt-10">"</span>. Then </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;format</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;x</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="s">"%1y/%2m/%3d</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="s">&nbsp;%01H:%02M:%06.3S"</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="C">#</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;"98/</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;7/</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;6</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="C">&nbsp;5:04:03.123"</span></span>
<!--l. 9604--></pre>
<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a id="x1-225000III"></a>Function style</h4>
<a id="Q1-1-446"></a>
<!--l. 9609--><p class="noindent">This form of the command is deprecated. Please see <span class="cmbx-10">set style function (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-299000III"><span class="cmbx-10">203</span><!--tex4ht:ref: set style function --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-225001"></a>.
</p><h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a id="x1-226000III"></a>Functions</h4>
<a id="Q1-1-448"></a>
<!--l. 9614--><p class="noindent">The <span class="cmbx-10">show functions </span>command lists all user-defined functions and their definitions.
<!--l. 9617--></p><p class="noindent">Syntax: </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">show</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;functions</span></span>
<!--l. 9621--></pre>
<!--l. 9624--><p class="noindent">For information about the definition and usage of functions in <span class="cmbx-10">gnuplot</span>, please see <span class="cmbx-10">expressions (p.</span><span class="cmbx-10">&nbsp;</span><a href="#x1-24000I"><span class="cmbx-10">28</span><!--tex4ht:ref: expressions --></a><span class="cmbx-10">)</span><a id="dx1-226001"></a>. See
also
<a href="http://www.gnuplot.info/demo/spline.html"><span class="cmtt-10">splines as user defined functions (spline.dem) </span></a>
and
<a href="http://www.gnuplot.info/demo/airfoil.html"><span class="cmtt-10">use of functions and complex variables for airfoils (airfoil.dem). </span></a>
<!--l. 9634--></p><p class="noindent">
</p><h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a id="x1-227000III"></a>Grid</h4>
<a id="Q1-1-450"></a>
<a id="dx1-227001"></a>
<a id="dx1-227002"></a>
<!--l. 9646--><p class="noindent">The <span class="cmbx-10">set grid </span>command allows grid lines to be drawn on the plot.
