<a id="dx1-396002"></a>
<!--l. 16202--><p class="noindent">The <span class="cmbx-10">cgi </span>and <span class="cmbx-10">hcgi </span>terminal drivers support SCO CGI drivers. <span class="cmbx-10">hcgi </span>is for printers; the environment variable
CGIPRNT must be set. <span class="cmbx-10">cgi </span>may be used for either a display or hardcopy; the environment variable CGIDISP is
checked, first, then CGIPRNT. These terminals have no options.
