<h4 class="likesubsectionHead"><a id="x1-415000IV"></a>Emf</h4>
<a id="Q1-1-825"></a>
<a id="dx1-415001"></a>
                                                                                         
                                                                                         
<!--l. 16841--><p class="noindent">The <span class="cmbx-10">emf </span>terminal generates an Enhanced Metafile Format file. This file format is recognized by many Windows
