of graphs in the horizontal and vertical directions; these default to unity.
<!--l. 17942--></p><p class="noindent">Example: </p><pre class="prettyprint"><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="k">set</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;terminal</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;imagen</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;portrait</span></span><span class="cmtt-10"><span class="p">&nbsp;</span><span class="o">[</span><span class="n">2</span><span class="o">,</span><span class="n">3</span><span class="o">]</span></span>
<!--l. 17946--></pre>
